title: Google brings Google Duo Live Sharing and YouTube previews in Messages to the new Samsung Galaxy S22 series
content:
Samsung just lifted the covers off six new flagship devices, including three Galaxy S22 series smartphones and three Galaxy Tab S8 series tablets. The new devices feature top-of-the-line hardware, including the latest chipsets from Qualcomm and Samsung, impressive high refresh rate displays, faster charging capabilities, and more.
